<section class="u-black text-center py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <img class="u-icon-image mb-3" src="images/orange-logo.png" />
    <h1>Learn how to play Dota 2</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 mb-0">You Can Do It!</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container my-5">
  <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="col col-md-8">
      <div class="u-light p-5">
        <h5>Authors Note</h5>
        <p>
          Thank you for checking out my tutorial of Dota 2. This game means a whole awful lot to me. However, I know it can be scary to get into because of its complexity and/or notorious community.
        </p>
        <p>
          But I am here to tell you that for the right person Dota does not have to be a chore to learn. The fun starts the moment to get into it and begin playing.
        </p>
        <p>
          Allow this guide to be a useful companion on your journey to learning one of the most rewarding competitive multiplayer games ever made.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-0">
          Good luck and have fun!<br><br>
          @DirtyChump
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="u-black py-5">
  <section class="container">
